text: First Suite in E-flat for Military Band is a piece of music by Gustav Holst. It was written in 1909 and had its first performance in 1920. There are three movements: "Chaconne", "Intermezzo", and "March". The suite is thought a cornerstone of music for military band. Category:Compositions by Gustav Holst Category:Suites
title: First Suite in E-flat for Military Band
